  "body": "Hello, \r\n\r\nThank you for your work. \r\nI want to test a dApp and I have tried to deploy a Besu network on a free tier Ubuntu EC2 AWS server with Docker, it went well until I wanted to run `truffle migrate --reset --compile-all --network besu` \r\nThen I got an error message because I think it consumed too much memory. \r\n\r\nDo you know if it is possible to run any kind of Besu network on a free tier EC2 instance ? \r\n\r\nThank you, ",
